These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: tennis, volleyball, ice-hockey
1. Sport:volleyball is on the right of Sport:ice-hockey##1
2. Sport:tennis is on the far right##1
3. Sport:tennis is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | volleyball | tennis |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: cherry, banana, lime
1. Food:banana is in an odd position##4
2. Food:cherry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | cherry | lime | banana |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: puzzles, gardening, fishing
1. Hobby:gardening is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:gardening is on the left or right of Hobby:fishing##3
3. Hobby:fishing is on the right of Hobby:gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | puzzles | gardening | fishing |

 #################################
 
